Title: Elgin Depot Museum - Explore Bastrop County
Description: Elgin Depot Museum includes an extensive archive collection and is the repository for historic photographs in the community . Operated by the Elgin Historical Association, the museum is open Wednesday through Saturday from noon to 4 p.m.
